Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:12.88,Default,Ayumu,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:18.27,Default,Chino,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to clean this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:20.24,Default,Chino,0000,0000,0000,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:00.41,Title1E10,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(671,249)}The Unfaithful Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.93,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.88,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for welcoming me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.22,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,my human toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.80,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Kage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.18,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It's been forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.16,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Ririchiyo's fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.93,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You came back soon this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.35,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.75,Sign10A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hokkaido (M)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.92,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I was in Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.23,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,And I brought gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.90,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You get a dog collar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.61,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,And you, a candle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.61,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You get a whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.24,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always get a whip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.91,Sign10A,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Shikoku (S)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.91,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Shikoku, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.04,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.20,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Manacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.39,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You get a whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.00,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always get a whip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.69,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:16.08,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But Miketsukami and I \Nhave an engagement,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.14,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,so if you'll excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:17.79,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:18.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.38,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.93,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,For I have bought you a gift as well, sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:32.45,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fairly certain that last time, \NI told you I'd freeze you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.56,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever came near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.76,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,More ice fetish play, I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.66,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.74,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,She's dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.65,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:45.92,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.62,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.62,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:55.24,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It's a party! \NEnjoy it, my human toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.14,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This is my welcome back party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:04.52,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a dazzling orgy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:07.60,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Kage, you're wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.28,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Debau-che-ry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:09.28,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Ry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.53,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.19,Sign10A,Kagerou/txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(316,436)}Five Hours Later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.63,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.49,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo, here is some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.15,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Is it already that late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.77,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall take my leave, you pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.55,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It's already over?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.45,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Staying up late ruins your \Nlooks and your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.46,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It's positively sadistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.64,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Here he goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.25,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Fiancée of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.59,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I shall soon depart again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.42,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.27,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.34,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really expect me to agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.26,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't rush your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.76,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I also have an important matter \Nto discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.43,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,An important matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.47,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:02.34,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Let us have a long chat tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.52,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.62,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta! Karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.66,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.94,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Shee you later, Wahanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:20.12,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that man, it's gotten quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.71,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reschedule our appointment for \Ntomorrow, after I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:24.76,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.39,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.76,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.82,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll ask you to take me \Nhome afterward, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.86,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see her in the lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:53.36,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Roromiya just stayed with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:56.03,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I went to her room this morning, \Nbut she wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:06:00.08,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe she'd just \Nleft early for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.96,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he had something important
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.91,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,to discuss with me last time he came, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:08.88,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.81,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,And as the Assyrian Empire flourished...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:20.65,Inuboku-flashback,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not Soushi's old master and your fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:24.69,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Miketsukami already knows
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.41,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,that he's my fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.00,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:35.12,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,he's never brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:39.61,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he isn't \Ninterested in me that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.46,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.77,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,you got engaged to that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.02,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's something our parents decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.12,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,But weren't you writing to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.92,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:00.08,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like there was anything \NI wanted to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.60,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote to him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.09,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.50,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I would run home from school, \Nas if I were escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.30,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I couldn't stand \Nto be at home, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.16,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So I stood in front of the mailbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.16,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,As if I were praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:40.86,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That little letter contained words
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.52,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,and sentences meant just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:47.69,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That alone made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.15,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1015)}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.48,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's grab something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:58.65,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd forgotten about the letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.75,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.54,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,My fiancée, we met most recently \Nbut last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.80,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to fetch you in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.10,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I shall treat you to Chinese food, my fiancée!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:12.93,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.34,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:15.34,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.02,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.64,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Peking duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.11,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first thing out of your mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This is kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:30.90,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.15,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Peking duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.91,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.33,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for Miketsukami—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.08,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:42.50,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I told him not to bother since \NI'm taking my fiancée for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.25,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Our coffee appointment...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.36,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.97,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Fiancée? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.40,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of upholding \Nthat agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.08,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.36,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,He and I are not so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.01,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.80,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.21,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.21,0:09:04.84,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,He's a sadist, just like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.61,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fitting people into your little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.34,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I've told you that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.26,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't merely my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.61,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Everything can be divided by \Nmasochism or sadism.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.91,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm sure I've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.82,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.33,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That mother's a sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.45,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Her kid's a sadist, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.09,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That salaryman is a masochist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.71,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That dog is a total masochist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.24,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This chauffeur is a masochist...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:27.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.05,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.66,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head on the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.35,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.06,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This glass is entirely sadistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.67,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,But we aren't getting anywhere. \NI suppose it's this traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.84,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,And that means this road \Nis a bit of a sadist, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.26,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Chinese Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.43,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This table doesn't rotate too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:44.59,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Rather sadistic, I'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.77,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just a facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.47,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It's a masochist that yearns to be dominated!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.24,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Kage seems to be enjoying himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:51.11,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not enjoying myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.61,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.57,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:58.82,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I shall spin you, and spin you, \Nand spin you some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:01.83,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarium
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.41,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,The Southern Rockhopper Penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.33,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,At first, he appears to be the \Ncute masochistic type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.49,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, however, he is \Nan uncontrollable sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.82,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.00,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.35,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Sardines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:13.76,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Flounder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:14.92,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.84,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,They look delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.76,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Tea Time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:21.10,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This cocoa's sweet. Masochist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:22.66,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.18,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Ginger ale is spicy. Sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.10,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Movies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.43,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,The movie theater is dark. Masochist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.51,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's coming right at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.94,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It's 3D! Sadistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.24,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.19,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:35.61,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This mannequin's a cool beauty. Sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.19,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,But this one's a masochist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.28,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.03,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Night Sights
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.77,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,The view at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.95,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Super-sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.41,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.31,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.63,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.70,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,so return my bag and cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.01,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Is this mutiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.49,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Is this mutinous super-masochism?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.72,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! I like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.22,Sign10B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:06.05,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He dragged me all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.49,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's already 10:30 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.43,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to meet Miketsukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.00,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He always wants to be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.97,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make him feel lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.24,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is he mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.88,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Am I reading too much into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.88,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I should at least \Nwrite and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.17,Sign10C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Sending
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:34.80,Sign10C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Message Sent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:54.44,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm waiting too eagerly for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:58.82,Sign10D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(508,1)}Waiting for a Reply
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:58.82,Sign10E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(483,1)}Uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.82,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He usually writes back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.57,Sign10E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Uneasy \N\N\NUneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.57,Sign10E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.57,Sign10D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,10 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.57,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This is not unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.45,Sign10D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}30 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.45,Sign10E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Uneasy Uneasy Uneasy... \NUneasy Uneasy Uneasy... \NUneasy Uneasy Uneasy... \NUneasy Uneasy Uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.53,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This could happen any day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:09.24,Sign10D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,50 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.73,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he angry, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:09.24,Default - Margin,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I should meet him and apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.97,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't call on him this late...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:14.47,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He did say that he stays up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.50,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.75,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.63,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Could I really meet him and \Nproperly apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:25.46,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, maybe he's just busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:28.77,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, this hasn't \Never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:29.43,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.18,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.10,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.50,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up leaving my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.27,Sign10D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Apology Gift
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.95,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.92,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced apologizing nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.84,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just have to put my heart \Ninto it, and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:48.58,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,F-First, say, "I'm sorry to \Ndisturb you so late."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.25,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.53,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He's in normal clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.46,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.30,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,His hair's wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:01.49,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.51,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:06.28,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is awkward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.67,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:10.87,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry to disturb you so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should start with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.19,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't keep our appointment today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.18,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,which wasn't my intention at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:20.04,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I said in my test run at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:20.93,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.36,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Your uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.92,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You're still wearing your school uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.81,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,so you two were together until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.57,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.29,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.47,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he hasn't told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.21,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Told me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He only sputtered nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:44.50,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You need not apologize to me for \Nanything you do with Mr. Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you actually like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.17,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?! Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.23,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Then you seem to be quite good
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:01.40,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,at unintentionally sending men \Nthe wrong signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:05.07,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to pick a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.49,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:12.71,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am your faithful dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.79,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Would I bite the hand that feeds me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember that you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:25.66,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,have made a contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:36.64,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were to reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.07,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're not yourself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.32,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,"Could it be that you actually like him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.04,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.71,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go home the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:01.92,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:04.56,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.31,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with Miketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.66,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.70,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.90,Sign10E,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I...  \N\NMiketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.85,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:02.63,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,A bath where you gaze at humanity below. \NNow that is exceptional...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.62,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I love looking down on people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:08.04,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I know you do, Mr. Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.46,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.38,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You're naughty. Don't sneak up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:17.87,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't end up talking \Nabout it yesterday, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:18.81,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.81,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to say anything \Nwith the others there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:27.02,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It is a petty issue to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:30.53,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,but I suppose it is something \Nwomen care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.69,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,My fiancée will soon be sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.99,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Couples should have no \Nreservations between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:39.03,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kagerou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:42.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible for you \Nto avoid mentioning it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.40,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do anything in my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:49.72,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,For her? Or for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.80,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, your "anything" bores me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.26,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You really would do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.93,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You'd do any embarrassing \Ntask with a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.89,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:03.18,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel like I am beneath you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.60,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I never liked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.60,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.03,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,you are begging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.32,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,But I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.43,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Truly being on your \Nknees for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:29.75,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:33.06,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:37.01,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have been on my knees \Nmany times in your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:38.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:43.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,the issue I bring before you \Nis no petty matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:19:00.57,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,So I shall ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.08,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.00,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:29.66,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Your strikes suggest that you're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.44,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to get attacked, once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:41.16,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you should enjoy my treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.86,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:50.06,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy a drink, and get some \Nmorning sun while I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:55.75,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Could you not find it within your
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:59.08,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,great heart to consider this weak and \Ninsignificant servant's request?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:01.36,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Weak and insignificant, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.21,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You're a stubborn, shameless super-sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.01,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You deceive everyone with \Nyour aura of purity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:07.88,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality you're a ****!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:11.08,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Admit it, and I shall consider your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.28,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:14.37,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall accept it, and bear the dishonor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:16.80,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I deceive everyone with my aura of purity,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.69,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality, I'm a **** pervert—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.45,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:22.73,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You should do this outside! You're adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.17,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:27.01,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, my bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:28.52,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me your salutations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.91,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from that man, \Nand sheathe your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:31.66,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:33.33,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:35.00,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.25,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Me? The aggressor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:38.75,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I like it! I like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:42.92,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami would never hurt \Nanyone without cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:46.53,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I see you trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:49.84,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're cut from the same cloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.14,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should say we're guilty \Nof the same offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.65,0:22:55.27,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:57.39,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,You should ask him directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:23:02.90,Default,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,That man is good at deceiving others, \Nbut he probably cannot lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:05.20,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:09.50,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I can lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:11.41,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:15.54,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I intended to keep it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:16.58,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.80,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather tell you myself than have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:23.67,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,you hear it from another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:27.95,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo, it is as Mr. Kagerou says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.91,0:23:30.24,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.64,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,been deceiving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:42.40,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:43.94,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:46.98,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have been lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:50.61,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I deceived and betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:54.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could hide it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.99,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But... But, Miss Ririchiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:24:01.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,all I wish for is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:05.25,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on {\i1}Inu X Boku Secret Service{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:06.51,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Kagerou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.92,Inuboku-next-ep-titleE10,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kagerou
